    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>An act of documentation via photography to record the conditon or state of an object or the status of a project. Examples include excavations or art conservation treatments.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
